WEBVTT

01:49.526 --> 01:51.778
Everyone, fall back and cover my brother.

01:51.861 --> 01:54.989
Don’t screw with me! I’m the one
taking that monster’s head!

01:55.073 --> 01:57.450
Beheading a Tensen
won't kill it, you know.

01:57.534 --> 02:00.662
I know that! It’s just a figure of speech!

02:00.745 --> 02:02.413
‎Just do what my brother says!

02:02.497 --> 02:03.957
- Shut up, man-woman!
- You idiots.

02:12.423 --> 02:13.967
Stay back, idiots.

02:21.474 --> 02:23.101
We’re stuck on the defensive.

02:23.184 --> 02:24.185
Brother!

02:24.269 --> 02:25.603
I told you to stay back!

02:26.271 --> 02:29.190
Tentacles and spores.
I can’t handle all of them!

02:29.274 --> 02:30.108
Shit.

02:30.692 --> 02:33.194
If they fuse, that means
twice the attacks, huh.

02:33.945 --> 02:37.115
The runt and the old man
are terrible at handling Tao.

02:37.198 --> 02:39.617
Toma doesn't have mutual overcoming Tao.

02:40.201 --> 02:43.371
But I have mutual overcoming Tao
against Tao Fa.

02:43.454 --> 02:46.249
And I’ve got a secret plan
for dealing with Ju Fa.

02:46.332 --> 02:49.836
Am I the only one
who can kill this monster?

02:51.588 --> 02:53.089
In the case of water Tao,

02:53.172 --> 02:54.966
the things that house it,

02:55.049 --> 02:58.970
for example, chestnuts and soybeans,
the kidneys and the bladder,

02:59.637 --> 03:01.472
gather them all and ferment them,

03:01.556 --> 03:03.725
and you create a liquor that contains Tao.

03:04.434 --> 03:08.479
Write the target’s name
on a talisman infused with incense.

03:08.563 --> 03:12.233
Strong Tao-bearing catalysts
resonate with each other,

03:12.317 --> 03:15.737
revealing the target’s fortune
or misfortune and their current form.

03:16.779 --> 03:17.780
Chobe.

03:18.323 --> 03:20.491
YAMADA ASAEMON TOMA

03:21.159 --> 03:23.745
I see a bad omen surrounding
your younger brother.

03:30.668 --> 03:33.254
I’ll handle this myself.

03:33.338 --> 03:36.216
Same as always. No problem.

03:38.968 --> 03:40.261
Livestock...

03:41.054 --> 03:41.888
I’ll kill you.

03:51.022 --> 03:52.190
Are you okay, Brother?

04:00.949 --> 04:02.742
This is going to work, right?

04:02.825 --> 04:04.494
Yes, I'm sure of it.

04:14.212 --> 04:15.046
See?

04:15.672 --> 04:18.299
If I strengthen
my "metal" with your "earth,"

04:18.383 --> 04:20.677
I can overcome Tao Fa’s Tao.

04:20.760 --> 04:23.054
It even works between yang types?

04:24.639 --> 04:26.057
It seems so.

04:26.140 --> 04:27.058
Let's put the pressure on--

04:27.141 --> 04:31.312
I'm the one getting that monster!

04:35.233 --> 04:36.067
‎Shit!

04:36.150 --> 04:37.527
You're the one who's shit!

04:37.610 --> 04:39.904
I told you I'm the one
getting that monster!

04:39.988 --> 04:41.155
Don’t get in the way!

04:41.239 --> 04:43.074
If you get wet, your wounds will open up!

04:43.157 --> 04:45.576
- I'm fine, you idiot!
- My brother told you to stay back...

04:45.660 --> 04:48.204
I’ve never seen him
argue with someone like that.

04:49.163 --> 04:51.416
Not even back when he was a bandit.

04:52.750 --> 04:55.962
He was just a kid
who copied everything I did.

05:10.560 --> 05:13.479
- Hey, idiots. Look up.
- Huh?

05:39.964 --> 05:42.550
It... flipped over?

05:42.633 --> 05:44.385
Guess they switched offense and defense.

05:44.969 --> 05:47.388
It’s letting its injured half rest.

05:47.472 --> 05:51.517
At this rate, cutting it won’t get us
anywhere. Looks like we’ll have to destroy

05:51.601 --> 05:53.895
both Ju Fa’s and Tao Fa’s
Tandens at the same time.

05:54.520 --> 05:56.898
- Old man, you’re coming with me.
- Huh?

05:57.607 --> 05:59.817
We split up into two groups.

05:59.901 --> 06:03.279
We’ll kill Ju Fa. I’ve got a secret plan.

06:03.988 --> 06:06.574
You guys handle Tao Fa.

06:06.657 --> 06:08.910
The method from earlier should work.

06:09.535 --> 06:11.204
Understood, Brother.

06:11.287 --> 06:13.039
So specifically, how should we move--

06:13.706 --> 06:17.126
You ask me about everything way too much!

06:17.210 --> 06:19.170
Hey, Brother!

06:23.132 --> 06:26.761
I told you I was leaving
everything to you.

06:26.844 --> 06:28.054
Think for yourself.

06:29.680 --> 06:31.766
You can do it by now, right?

06:36.771 --> 06:39.148
I don’t need to be micromanaged.

06:39.232 --> 06:40.942
I’m counting on you.

06:41.025 --> 06:42.276
Huh?

06:42.360 --> 06:46.697
Without the famed sword of Eight Provinces
Unparalleled, my plan won’t work.

06:46.781 --> 06:49.659
I-if that’s the case...

06:50.159 --> 06:53.538
He always has the same look on his face
when he manipulates subordinates.

07:01.546 --> 07:03.631
He's desperate to protect her, huh?

07:03.714 --> 07:05.341
I can sympathize with that a little.

07:06.092 --> 07:09.846
But sometimes the ones you want to protect
are stronger than you think.

07:09.929 --> 07:12.181
If you don't let go,
you'll end up suffocating them.

07:12.682 --> 07:14.934
I’ll cut them from each other.

07:15.017 --> 07:17.603
Dying together would suit them just fine.

07:36.289 --> 07:37.331
Brother!

07:37.415 --> 07:40.460
They’re reacting simultaneously
to movements from all four of us.

07:40.543 --> 07:42.837
There’s no opening
to strike their Tandens.

07:43.588 --> 07:46.048
The runt and the man-woman! Cover me!

07:46.132 --> 07:46.966
What?

07:47.049 --> 07:48.843
I’ll create an opening for you to attack!

07:48.926 --> 07:50.344
What are you planning to do?

07:50.428 --> 07:52.972
I don’t know... but let’s trust him!

08:04.192 --> 08:05.610
Gantetsusai!

08:05.693 --> 08:08.029
I'm fine. Push forward!

08:10.865 --> 08:12.450
There's no way he's fine.

08:12.533 --> 08:15.203
He’s just bluffing with bravado.

08:15.286 --> 08:18.956
Countless lacerations,
contusions, internal injuries.

08:19.582 --> 08:22.460
After so many battles,
he’s reaching his limit.

08:33.387 --> 08:34.388
Toma!

08:36.891 --> 08:40.603
Your Tao is a key part
of my brother’s plan.

08:40.686 --> 08:41.771
Don’t just stand there!

08:41.854 --> 08:43.064
I-I am gratef--

08:43.147 --> 08:44.440
Enough, let’s move!

08:50.988 --> 08:53.074
Everyone's all beaten and cut up.

08:53.157 --> 08:55.076
But if we miss this chance...

08:55.159 --> 08:56.577
We’ll never win!

09:00.873 --> 09:03.209
Ready when you are, brats.

09:12.093 --> 09:13.719
The Gate Slash!

09:17.056 --> 09:18.140
It’s regenerating!

09:18.224 --> 09:20.518
Don’t let this opening slip, Toma!

09:21.060 --> 09:22.895
Tao Fa’s Tanden is...

09:23.563 --> 09:25.356
Lower right, 5 p.m.!

10:09.525 --> 10:11.777
That’s enough... enough...

10:15.781 --> 10:18.284
T... Tao Fa!

10:21.078 --> 10:22.747
You’re still not dead?

10:22.830 --> 10:25.124
My Tao doesn’t overcome yours.

10:25.207 --> 10:28.002
To kill you, I have to stop you
from regenerating

10:28.085 --> 10:29.879
after destroying your Tanden.

10:39.555 --> 10:42.475
- Brother?
- My hidden ace.

10:44.101 --> 10:47.897
It was originally meant
to kill that fire ninja runt,

10:50.775 --> 10:52.318
but I’ll use it on you instead!

10:54.987 --> 10:59.241
That Tao-infused liquor they all use...

10:59.325 --> 11:02.745
Water Tao. I stole some of it.

11:04.330 --> 11:06.999
I’m good at playing people.

11:09.835 --> 11:11.754
The effect’s immediate.

11:11.837 --> 11:14.757
You can't regenerate with the effects
of mutual overcoming, right?

11:14.840 --> 11:18.260
Running your mouth about
Tao and mutual overcoming.

11:18.344 --> 11:21.639
Did you really think I was serious
about being on your side?

11:23.891 --> 11:25.768
Serves you right.

11:25.851 --> 11:28.479
Regret the day you picked
a fight with us brothers

11:28.562 --> 11:31.524
and die.

11:32.191 --> 11:33.651
He has poor taste.

11:33.734 --> 11:35.027
Poor taste?

11:35.111 --> 11:37.905
My brother’s a total villain.

11:43.536 --> 11:45.955
Don’t just mercy-kill him like that.

11:46.038 --> 11:48.249
Do you pity him, old man?

11:50.376 --> 11:53.796
I told you I'd be the one
finishing off the monster, didn't I?

12:01.762 --> 12:04.181
I’m not enjoying this at all.

12:05.349 --> 12:08.185
I had fun, girlie.

12:10.020 --> 12:15.192
I’m sorry... T... Tao Fa... I... I...

12:16.527 --> 12:17.945
couldn't protect you...

12:19.738 --> 12:20.948
I’m sorry...

12:26.287 --> 12:27.746
Tao Fa...

12:31.459 --> 12:34.753
I’m glad I was paired with you... Ju Fa.

12:44.430 --> 12:47.433
I never thought we’d all survive.

12:50.311 --> 12:52.062
Is everyone else okay?

12:54.565 --> 12:56.525
‎A FEW MOMENTS AGO

12:58.027 --> 13:01.989
Just so you know, I'm not here to fight.

13:03.115 --> 13:05.993
I was just told to stay here
and watch the place.

13:07.453 --> 13:08.621
So...

13:09.914 --> 13:12.500
If you don’t interfere,
I won’t do anything either.

13:13.375 --> 13:14.877
But if you do...

13:14.960 --> 13:16.420
I’ll crush you.

13:21.842 --> 13:24.512
Who's that? They're reading a book?

13:24.595 --> 13:28.516
No doubt about it.
This is the Ren Tan Palace.

13:28.599 --> 13:30.643
But... Rien's not here.

13:31.268 --> 13:33.646
Where is Rien, Gui Fa?

13:34.647 --> 13:37.525
Rien left just a moment ago.

13:38.192 --> 13:40.402
I was only entrusted with this.

13:40.486 --> 13:41.654
"This"?

13:45.741 --> 13:49.995
Gui Fa’s shyness is intense.
Even worse than before.

13:51.121 --> 13:54.542
That’s Meimokuho,
a ritual using Tao-bearing objects

13:54.625 --> 13:58.295
as a medium to read fate and fortune.

13:58.379 --> 14:01.799
You see their form through the talisman.

14:02.383 --> 14:04.677
I knew you'd come here.

14:05.261 --> 14:07.638
I was waiting here for you.

14:08.847 --> 14:10.808
Then if we destroy that,

14:10.891 --> 14:13.310
they won’t be able to read our movements.

14:15.396 --> 14:17.648
Tao attack! From above.

14:18.482 --> 14:19.942
It feels like we’re being crushed.

14:20.609 --> 14:23.571
Let go of your sword.

14:23.654 --> 14:24.822
Sagiri!

14:29.827 --> 14:32.204
You can still move? Impressive.

14:33.247 --> 14:35.207
But under Rien's orders,

14:35.791 --> 14:37.960
if you do want to fight, I'll crush you.

14:40.880 --> 14:43.215
We do not intend to fight.

14:43.299 --> 14:46.719
First, please allow me to apologize.

14:47.803 --> 14:51.682
For intruding on the island
and for everything that's followed.

14:51.765 --> 14:55.102
Though it was through ignorance,
we are also to blame.

14:55.853 --> 14:57.479
We apologize for that.

14:57.563 --> 14:58.689
Sagiri.

14:59.481 --> 15:00.691
How noble of you.

15:01.442 --> 15:05.070
But I can’t deny
my guts are boiling with rage.

15:06.864 --> 15:10.618
From what I hear, you’re the ones
who lured humans here.

15:10.701 --> 15:14.246
By that logic, this conflict
is entirely self-inflicted.

15:15.623 --> 15:17.374
But to just write it off
as self-inflicted,

15:18.208 --> 15:21.045
haven’t we all lost
far too much to do that?

15:21.545 --> 15:25.007
That’s why I came to stop the fighting.

15:25.549 --> 15:28.010
Any more killing is pointless.

15:28.093 --> 15:30.220
We’ll leave the island quietly.

15:31.180 --> 15:33.474
Please let us go.

15:33.557 --> 15:37.394
The elixir and the shogunate
can wait for now.

15:37.478 --> 15:39.688
Survival is the priority right now!

15:40.189 --> 15:43.484
Her Tao just spiked.

15:46.904 --> 15:47.988
The pressure’s gone.

15:48.822 --> 15:51.450
You can go. I don't really care.

15:51.533 --> 15:53.827
I was just told to guard this place,

15:53.911 --> 15:55.746
and I wasn’t interested anyway.

15:56.538 --> 15:57.623
- Then...
- But...

15:57.706 --> 16:00.292
It’s probably meaningless now,

16:00.376 --> 16:02.378
even if you do return to Japan.

16:03.462 --> 16:04.880
What do you mean?

16:06.715 --> 16:09.760
You asked where Rien was, right, Mei?

16:12.096 --> 16:16.517
He’s just showing illusions
with Tao. It's not real.

16:21.021 --> 16:23.899
Rien went beneath the main palace,

16:23.983 --> 16:25.526
to the water gate.

16:27.444 --> 16:30.030
He's preparing to set sail with the Doshi.

16:30.114 --> 16:33.033
Set sail? For what?

16:37.871 --> 16:41.166
To turn all the people of Japan into Tan.

16:41.250 --> 16:42.918
How?

16:43.585 --> 16:45.546
They'll load the completed Tan seeds

16:46.213 --> 16:49.800
into the Paradise Butterflies
and put them on the ship.

16:51.802 --> 16:54.304
They’ll hatch in Japan...

16:55.389 --> 16:56.682
and scatter.

17:33.427 --> 17:36.346
Their range is thousands of miles.
Their numbers are thousands.

17:37.639 --> 17:40.350
In the blink of an eye,
they'll cover all of Japan.

17:52.404 --> 17:55.616
Humans turned into external
Tan flowers will link together...

17:55.699 --> 17:58.118
forming one massive being.

17:58.827 --> 18:00.287
The divine beast, "Pangu."

18:01.038 --> 18:05.459
From there, Rien will cultivate
the perfect Tan he's been after.

18:10.756 --> 18:12.674
Sagiri!

18:12.758 --> 18:14.176
It's pointless, isn't it?

18:14.259 --> 18:16.428
You’ll just turn into flowers
even if you do get back.

18:21.975 --> 18:25.437
Why? What reason is there to go this far?

18:26.146 --> 18:27.147
"Why"?

18:29.191 --> 18:30.943
Ah, I got it.

18:31.026 --> 18:32.694
Could it be...

18:32.778 --> 18:34.154
you think there’s a reason?

18:34.238 --> 18:37.449
That we could talk, understand each other?

18:38.367 --> 18:42.454
I don’t know what you think you know
about us, but you’re very mistaken.

18:42.538 --> 18:45.666
Humans are nothing more
than materials for elixirs.

18:45.749 --> 18:48.335
We feel about as much attachment
as one would to small animals.

18:48.418 --> 18:52.047
That’s not true! The Master’s research

18:52.131 --> 18:54.591
was for the emperor and the people!

18:54.675 --> 18:57.719
Using human lives is wrong! You know that!

18:57.803 --> 19:00.430
Things are different now, Mei.

19:00.514 --> 19:01.598
Since then,

19:02.683 --> 19:04.601
we’ve tested bait many times.

19:05.185 --> 19:07.271
Hundreds of years ago,

19:07.855 --> 19:11.775
for the first time, humans, ones
from the outside, came to the island.

19:13.694 --> 19:16.864
That’s when we learned

19:17.823 --> 19:19.908
just how wonderful humans are.

19:21.952 --> 19:25.122
Far more fragile than expected.

19:25.205 --> 19:27.875
And possessing Tao of far
higher quality than expected.

19:28.917 --> 19:30.752
Much better material.

19:30.836 --> 19:33.755
Much more wonderful material
than wooden dolls.

19:36.592 --> 19:39.511
Ran was captivated by their beauty.

19:39.595 --> 19:42.139
Mu Dan seemed delighted as well.

19:42.222 --> 19:44.183
Ju Fa and Tao Fa too

19:44.266 --> 19:48.270
realized that humans were the fastest way
to complete their training.

19:48.353 --> 19:51.273
Humans are beings full of hesitation.

19:51.356 --> 19:53.567
Hesitation is the essence of Tao.

19:53.650 --> 19:55.944
Wavering between extremes.

19:56.028 --> 19:58.280
That is the beauty of humanity.

19:58.864 --> 20:00.282
Love and hate.

20:00.365 --> 20:02.284
Life and death.

20:02.367 --> 20:05.412
We Tensen have neither love nor death.

20:05.495 --> 20:08.832
Now that we’ve come this far,
seeking materials other than humans

20:08.916 --> 20:10.250
is unthinkable.

20:11.251 --> 20:14.546
Especially now that
the elixir is complete.

20:15.130 --> 20:18.050
Understanding each other
now is impossible.

20:18.133 --> 20:22.054
If you just want to ignore
what’s happening here, fine.

20:22.137 --> 20:24.181
But a truce is meaningless.

20:24.765 --> 20:29.019
At this point, all we can do
is steal from one another.

20:33.065 --> 20:35.025
While we talk...

20:35.108 --> 20:36.818
YAMADA ASAEMON SHION

20:36.902 --> 20:38.820
...someone else will be taken again.

20:49.414 --> 20:51.291
‎YAMADA ASAEMON SHION

20:51.375 --> 20:52.584
Nurugai...

20:53.460 --> 20:54.461
How many times?

20:59.132 --> 20:59.967
‎2...

21:00.926 --> 21:02.344
215...

21:03.053 --> 21:05.138
You cut him 215 times!

21:07.432 --> 21:10.227
You killed him 215 times.

21:14.189 --> 21:17.985
His regeneration is weakening,
just like he said.

21:18.860 --> 21:22.239
Without a mutually overcoming Tao,
you cannot kill your opponent.

21:22.823 --> 21:27.369
But is there no other way
to corner a Tensen without that?

21:27.452 --> 21:30.372
Then what about exhausting
them through regeneration?

21:31.039 --> 21:33.875
If we repeat it rapidly in a short
time span, it seems to slow down.

21:34.459 --> 21:37.629
Draining their Tao with regeneration...
I don’t think it’s possible.

21:38.213 --> 21:39.506
A hundred times...

21:39.589 --> 21:41.883
A thousand times,
they could regenerate maybe.

21:41.967 --> 21:44.052
Cutting someone down a thousand times?

21:44.136 --> 21:45.679
And with magic tricks?

21:45.762 --> 21:46.972
With Tao.

21:47.055 --> 21:49.516
That’s impossible for a normal person.

22:00.277 --> 22:03.196
Sensei! You can't anymore!

22:03.280 --> 22:06.199
A thousand times... was it?

22:06.283 --> 22:08.577
Seems like we won’t need
that many after all.

22:22.799 --> 22:23.884
Damn it!

22:23.967 --> 22:24.885
Wait, Nurugai!

22:27.804 --> 22:29.514
No need to chase him recklessly.

22:29.598 --> 22:31.516
He's exhausted.

22:31.600 --> 22:33.393
He can't recover right away.

22:33.477 --> 22:36.772
Let’s finish this
carefully and definitively.

22:40.358 --> 22:44.780
What are you? You’re not normal!

22:48.158 --> 22:50.243
Those who take from others
cannot understand.

22:51.495 --> 22:55.248
Those who are taken from...
cannot ever forget!

24:23.003 --> 24:25.881
Subtitle translation by: Maslin Friedman
